4. External Tool Interfaces (Specifications)

Zig Commitment Tool (zig-commitment)

Input (stdin JSON):

```json
{
  "action": "create_commitment",
  "code_hash": "<hex-encoded 32-byte hash>",
  "style_vector": [0.12, -0.45, ...],  // 256 floats
  "author_public_key": "<hex-encoded 32-byte key>"
}
```
